<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Rent Agreement</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #000;
            background-color: #fff;
        }
        
        .page {
            width: 210mm;
            min-height: 297mm;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 25mm 20mm;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            background-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            text-align: right;
            font-size: 11px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #666;
        }
        
        .title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: underline;
            margin: 30px 0 40px 0;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }
        
        .section {
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: justify;
            text-indent: 30px;
        }
        
        .section.no-indent {
            text-indent: 0;
        }
        
        .clause {
            margin: 15px 0;
            padding-left: 0;
            text-align: justify;
        }
        
        .clause-number {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        
        .signatures {
            margin-top: 60px;
        }
        
        .signature-section {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-top: 50px;
            align-items: flex-end;
        }
        
        .signature-box {
            text-align: center;
            width: 220px;
        }
        
        .signature-line {
            height: 60px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #000;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .witnesses {
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
        
        .witness-line {
            margin: 15px 0;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
            width: 250px;
            height: 25px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-end;
        }
        
        .page-break-content {
            page-break-before: always;
        }
        
        .page-break {
            page-break-before: always;
        }
        
        .continued {
            text-align: right;
            font-size: 11px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-style: italic;
        }
        
        .witness-header {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        
        .final-section {
            margin: 30px 0;
            text-align: justify;
        }
        
        strong {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .and-section {
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 30px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .agreement-header {
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 30px 0;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        
        @media print {
            body {
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0;
            }
            .page {
                width: 100%;
                min-height: auto;
                margin: 0;
                padding: 20mm 15mm;
                box-shadow: none;
            }
        }
        
        @media screen {
            body {
                background-color: #f5f5f5;
                padding: 20px 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="page">
        <div class="header">
            Prepared by Makaan.com
        </div>

        <div class="title">
            RENT AGREEMENT
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            This Rent Agreement is made on this <strong><%= new Date(SignatureSection.SignedDate).toLocaleDateString('en-IN', { day: 'numeric', month: 'long', year: 'numeric' }) %></strong> (date of rent agreement) by <strong><%= Landlord.FullName %></strong> S/o <strong><%= Landlord.FathersName || 'Not Specified' %></strong> (father's name of the landlord), Add: <strong><%= Landlord.Address %></strong> (residential address of the landlord). Herein after called the Lessor / Owner, Party Of the first part
        </div>

        <div class="and-section">
            AND
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <strong><%= TenantCompany.CompanyName %></strong> (Name of the proposed company), through its proposed director <strong><%= TenantCompany.DirectorName %></strong> (name of the director) called Lessee/Tenant, Party of the Second Part
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            That the expression of the term, Lessor/Owner and the Lessee/Tenant Shall mean and include their legal heirs successors, assigns, representative etc. Whereas the Lessor/Owner is the owner and in possession of the property No: <strong><%= PropertyDetails.PropertyNumber %></strong> <strong><%= TenantCompany.RegisteredAddress %></strong> (registered address of the company) and has agreed to let out the <strong><%= PropertyDetails.IncludedRooms %></strong> on said property, to the Lessee/Tenant and the Lessee/Tenant has agreed to take the same on rent of Rs. <strong><%= RentDetails.MonthlyRent %>/-</strong> (<strong><%= RentDetails.MonthlyRentInWords %></strong>) per month.
        </div>

        <div class="agreement-header">
            NOW THIS RENT AGREEMENT WITNESSETH AS UNDER:-
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <span class="clause-number">1.</span> That the Tenant/Lessee shall pay as the monthly rent of RS. <strong><%= RentDetails.MonthlyRent %>/-</strong> (<strong><%= RentDetails.MonthlyRentInWords %></strong>) per month, <%= RentDetails.PaymentTerms.toLowerCase() %>.
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <span class="clause-number">2.</span> That the Tenant/Lessee shall not sub–let any part of the above said demised premised premises to anyone else under any circumstances without the consent of Owner.
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <span class="clause-number">3.</span> That the Tenant/Lessee shall abide by all the bye-laws, rules and regulation, of the local authorities in respect of the demised premises and shall not do any illegal activities in the said demised premises.
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <span class="clause-number">4.</span> That this Lease is granted for a period of <strong><%= LeaseTerms.LeaseDurationMonths %> (<%= LeaseTerms.LeaseDurationMonths === 11 ? 'Eleven' : 'Twelve' %>)</strong> months only commencing from <strong><%= new Date(LeaseTerms.LeaseStartDate).toLocaleDateString('en-IN', { day: 'numeric', month: 'long', year: 'numeric' }) %></strong> (date of rent commencing from) and this lease <% if (LeaseTerms.IsRenewable) { %>can be extended further by both the parties with their mutual consent on the basis of prevailing rental value in the market<% } else { %>shall not be extended beyond the specified period<% } %>.
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <span class="clause-number">5.</span> That the Lessee shall pay Electricity & Water charge as per the proportionate consumption of the meter to the Lessor/Owner.
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <span class="clause-number">6.</span> That the Tenant/Lessee shall not be entitled to make structure in the rented premises except the installation of temporary decoration, wooden partition/cabin, air–conditioners etc. without the prior consent of the owner.
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <span class="clause-number">7.</span> That the Tenant/lessee can neither make addition/alteration in the said premises without the written consent of the owner, nor the lessee can sublet part or entire premises to any person(s)/firm(s)/company(s).
        </div>

        <div class="continued">
            Contd: 2/-
        </div>

        <div class="page-break-content">
            <div class="clause">
            <span class="clause-number">8.</span> That the Tenant/Lessee shall permit the Lessor/Owner or his Authorized agent to enter in to the said tenanted premises for inspection/general checking or to carry out the repair work, at any reasonable time.
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <span class="clause-number">9.</span> That the Tenant/Lessee shall keep the said premises in clean & hygienic condition and shall not do or causes to be done any act which may be a nuisance to other.
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <span class="clause-number">10.</span> That the Tenant/Lessees shall carry on all day to day minor repairs at his/her own cost.
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <span class="clause-number">11.</span> That this Agreement may be terminated before the expiry of this tenancy period by serving One month prior notice by either party for this intention.
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <span class="clause-number">12.</span> That the Lessee shall use the above said premises for Official Purpose Only.
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <span class="clause-number">13.</span> That the Lessee/Tenant Shall not store/Keep any offensive, dangerous, explosive or highly Inflammable articles in the said premises and shall not use the same for any unlawful activities.
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <span class="clause-number">14.</span> That the Lessee shall pay the one month's advance rent to the Lessor the same shall be adjusted in monthly rent.
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <span class="clause-number">15.</span> That both the parties have read over and understood all the contents of this agreement and have signed the same without any force or pressure from any side.
        </div>

        <div class="final-section">
            In WITNESS WHEREOF the lessor/Owner and the Tenant/Lessee have hereunto subscribed their hand at <strong><%= SignatureSection.SignedAt || 'Not Specified' %></strong> (place) on this the <strong><%= new Date(SignatureSection.SignedDate).toLocaleDateString('en-IN', { day: 'numeric', month: 'long', year: 'numeric' }) %></strong> (date of rent agreement) year first above Mentioned in presents of the following Witnesses
        </div>

        <div class="witnesses">
            <div class="witness-header">WITNESSES:-</div>
            <% if (SignatureSection.Witnesses && SignatureSection.Witnesses.length > 0) { %>
                <% SignatureSection.Witnesses.forEach((witness, index) => { %>
                    <div class="witness-line"><%= index + 1 %>. <%= witness.FullName || '' %></div>
                <% }); %>
                <% for (let i = SignatureSection.Witnesses.length; i < 2; i++) { %>
                    <div class="witness-line"><%= i + 1 %>. </div>
                <% } %>
            <% } else { %>
                <div class="witness-line">1. </div>
                <div class="witness-line">2. </div>
            <% } %>
        </div>

        <div class="signature-section">
            <div class="signature-box">
                <div class="signature-line"></div>
                <div><strong><%= Landlord.FullName %></strong></div>
                <div>Lessor</div>
            </div>
            <div class="signature-box">
                <div class="signature-line"></div>
                <div><strong><%= TenantCompany.CompanyName %></strong></div>
                <div>Lessee</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>